title: #142: Gender Bender (@LaurenHennessy)
itunes:title: Gender Bender with Lauren Hennessy
description: Lauren Hennessy came over to my NY apartment to tell me about what it's like to be a he/she. Lauren is a boy trapped in a girl's body. He's been that way since he was born. And you think you had it tough. Don't worry, this didn't get too serious or sad. Just two dudes talking about one of the dude's vaginas.
